title: But In The Trend 3/12: MLB,  NCAA, DOW, Disneyland, Toilet Paper, Ilhan Omar

description:
On this episode of But In The Trend Jack and Miles discuss the MLB getting cancelled, NCAA March Madness getting cancelled, the DOW had the biggest single drop since the 80’s, Disneyland IS closing (thankfully), toilet paper is just gone around the country, and Ilhan Omar got married!
